## Testing Patterns

- Backend tests use pytest with `tmp_path` fixtures
- `test_docx_parser.py` — creates .docx in-memory with python-docx
- `test_integration_docx.py` — full pipeline: parse → validate → render
- Outlook tests mock `win32com.client` at module level
- SMTP tests use `aiosmtpd` local server

## Dependencies

PySide6, pandas, openpyxl, Jinja2, pywin32 (Windows only), PyYAML, pytest, aiosmtpd, python-docx

## Known Issues

- Qt cocoa plugin requires `pip install --force-reinstall PySide6_Essentials` on macOS occasionally
- PyInstaller spec needs `pywin32` hidden import added for Windows packaging
- No GUI automation tests (pytest-qt) — manual UAT only
